{"tid":1630221,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"（解鎖新職業）元素領域師","createTime":"2019-10-06T11:48:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T08:14:55.000Z","uid":70901,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c4fc7ae67a979d13c48935888aa8963b3777b4a2","tid":1630221,"uid":70901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:48:53.000Z","msg":"正話出mk派貼紙比文宣組，拖住銀發經過幾個黨鐵出入口，見到好多結界師上緊鎖，但你地有冇唸過倒d食油或者稀釋洗潔精落樓梯或者入口位，第一難以清理，第二可以加強結界師嘅力量，物料又易買又平，周圍都可以入貨<br />\n<br />\n見文幫手推推，唔係下下面硬碰，反正黨鐵都唔比人入，唔洗怕tk"},{"pid":"26466c1d5bb6ff71719c6723dc42bbbaca91550f","tid":1630221,"uid":154063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:49:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3bfea2c24a29e7739e2d01204d7a76525a514fac","tid":1630221,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:49:41.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"5a0d7fe77ee35347b4db0807ad188e3d6ccff08d","tid":1630221,"uid":70901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c4fc7ae67a979d13c48935888aa8963b3777b4a2","tid":1630221,"uid":70901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:48:53.000Z","msg":"正話出mk派貼紙比文宣組，拖住銀發經過幾個黨鐵出入口，見到好多結界師上緊鎖，但你地有冇唸過倒d食油或者稀釋洗潔精落樓梯或者入口位，第一難以清理，第二可以加強結界師嘅力量，物料又易買又平，周圍都可以入貨<br />\n<br />\n見文幫手推推，唔係下下面硬碰，反正黨鐵都唔比人入，唔洗怕tk"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:52:50.000Z","msg":"唔洗下下硬碰硬"},{"pid":"a1be09c06c3e8c020255199671ab4c7329111a84","tid":1630221,"uid":70901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:53:05.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"58ba16dc5df5da9a6db4cf7c637ae01e8e25fbec","tid":1630221,"uid":70901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:54:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc38df88dd1b12400710355e1927201f80b949c8","tid":1630221,"uid":70901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:54:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef0086355a1e1a2d17a0042b91338d5131683221","tid":1630221,"uid":70901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:55:05.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"d8405ee7dc2b2d47a5ab90e95c1de8c8976f4d9d","tid":1630221,"uid":70901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:58:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df925bc2aecc41a9b261f061e2354c9c4c04d62c","tid":1630221,"uid":70901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:58:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"965f5cbdebcf847bc4e6b866c8480aff6c295b4f","tid":1630221,"uid":70901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:00:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"712e97150bb5b01a471c4dce244fde8d40650deb","tid":1630221,"uid":70901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:00:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e771cb145f8ab578a27958c607b293293c518608","tid":1630221,"uid":70901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,